// ============================================================
// inject_rtti_err_denylist_free.lox — Denylist blocks Free()
// ============================================================
// Setup: Delphi injects a TCustomer as global 'cust'.
//
// What this tests:
//   - Attempting to call Free() on an injected object from Lox
//   - The RTTI method denylist should block this with a runtime error
//   - Prevents scripts from destroying objects owned by the host
print cust.Name; // expect: Alice
cust.Free(); // expect runtime error: Method 'Free' is not callable from script.
